      "rationale": "Three mesh levels (2.1M, 5.8M, 14.2M cells) were evaluated using Richardson extrapolation. GCI for the relative hemolysis index was 3.2% between the medium and fine mesh, confirming discretization error is within acceptable bounds at MRL 2. The medium mesh (5.8M cells) was selected for production runs."
