      "rationale": "Five operating points (flow rates 2–6 L/min, rotational speeds 2000–3500 RPM) were tested experimentally and reproduced in simulation with inlet boundary conditions set from measured flow rates. Fluid properties (viscosity, density) matched ISO 10993-compliant blood analogue within 2% across all test temperatures."
