    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for Model Risk Level 2. The six non-assessed factors are explicitly scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 requirements. The CFD model correctly identifies worst-case hemolysis operating conditions with RH values below 1.0 across all five operating points, supporting the regulatory submission decision that the device performs comparably to the predicate on hemolysis. The credibility assessment is accepted for the stated COU.",
